'''Colonel Matos''' was [[Owen Hunt|Owen]], [[Megan Hunt|Megan]], and [[Teddy Altman|Teddy's]] Colonel during their 2007 tour of duty in Iraq.

==History==
The Colonel arrived at the Mobile Treatment Center in Fallujah and complimented Owen on his work with his troops. He then announced that [[John Matthews]] was number one in the stratification ranking, disappointing [[Megan Hunt|Megan]].

==Career==
He is a Colonel in the US Army.
